Texts.Chs: 我们到底要不要解决问题？如果解决不了，我就走。
Texts.Eng: Are mew going to fix things or what? I'll leave if not.

Texts.Chs: 你是不是擅自重新布置了我的房子？
Texts.Eng: Did you rearrange my house without purrmission?

Texts.Chs: 要么是别的猫用它们的超能力来骚扰我，要么是它们拿走了什么东西。
Texts.Eng: Either another cat's using their powers to mess with me, or mew took something.

Texts.Chs: 嘿！这是我的房子，我不想和别人分享！
Texts.Eng: Hey! This is my house. I don't want to share!

Texts.Chs: 我受够了！你是个糟糕的房东。
Texts.Eng: I've had enough of this! You're a terrible landlord.

Texts.Chs: 如果我不把这房子修好，我就另找地方住！
Texts.Eng: If mew don't fix this house, I'm finding another place to live!

Texts.Chs: 也许普通的家庭主妇喜欢在东西上打洞，但我不喜欢！请把它修好。
Texts.Eng: Maybe ordinary housecats like having holes in things, but I don't! Fix it please.

Texts.Chs: 我觉得我来错新房子了...
Texts.Eng: Methinks mew put that in the wrong house...

Texts.Chs: 连狗都不愿意待在这里，我走了。
Texts.Eng: Not even a dog would want to stay here. I'm out.

Texts.Chs: 完美的时间安排。我需要把房子修理一下。
Texts.Eng: Purrfect timing. I need some repairs done to the house.

Texts.Chs: 这个新的程序让我的通灵能力受到了干扰。请把它放回去。
Texts.Eng: This new setup is upsetting my psychic powers. Put it back, please.

Texts.Chs: 那些洞让天气进来了，请给我们修一修好吗？
Texts.Eng: Those holes are letting the weather in. Can mew repair it please?

Texts.Chs: 我们猫要求我们的房东付出更大的努力。
Texts.Eng: We cats demand a much higher effort from our landlords.

Texts.Chs: 为什么有人要闯进我的房子？
Texts.Eng: Why's someone else trying to mewve into my house?
